posting_body: ['$500 Off Move-In Special!', 'Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'At Landings at Sweetwater, our residents can find all that they need for a life of ease.', 'With a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes to choose from and a community filled with unique spaces, our Lithia Springs luxury apartments are sure to accommodate every lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will love the large walk-in closets, private patios, and gourmet kitchens.', 'Throughout the community, residents can take advantage of the state-of-the-art fitness center, stunning swimming pool, and indoor and outdoor entertainment areas.', 'No matter what their lifestyle is, our apartments for rent in Lithia Springs, GA are sure to suit the needs of our residents.', 'Amenities:', '-Planned Activities', '-Picnic Area', '-Grills', '-Playground', '-Garden Tubs', '-Frost Free Refrigerator', '-Clubhouse', '-Private Entrance', '-Car Wash Area', '-Pets Welcome', '-Large Patios/Balconies', '-High Speed Internet', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
